---
import { SITE } from '../consts';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AdSlot from '../components/ads/AdSlot.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description={`Privacy Policy for ${SITE.name} — how we handle your data, cookies and advertising.`}
>
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 820px; padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: {new Date().getFullYear()}</p>

    <section class="prose">
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how {SITE.name} (“we”, “us”) collects, uses and protects
        information when you use our website. By using the site, you agree to the practices described
        here.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Our tools run in your browser, so the values you enter into a calculator or converter are
        processed on your device and are <strong>not transmitted to us</strong>. We do not require an
        account and do not collect names, emails or other personal details through the tools
        themselves.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Logs &amp; analytics</h2>
      <p>
        Like most websites, our hosting provider may automatically record standard server logs
        (such as IP address, browser type, pages visited and timestamps) to operate and secure the
        site. We may use privacy-friendly, aggregated analytics that do not identify individual
        visitors.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Cookies &amp; advertising</h2>
      <p>
        We display advertisements served by Google AdSense. Google and its partners may use cookies
        to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites. These cookies help
        deliver relevant ads and measure their performance.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          You can review and manage ad personalization in
          <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          You can opt out of personalized advertising through the
          <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YourAdChoices</a> program.
        </li>
        <li>
          Learn more about how Google uses data in its
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">advertising partners</a> policy.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Third-party links</h2>
      <p>
        Our site may link to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of
        those sites; please review their policies independently.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Data security</h2>
      <p>
        Because most processing happens on your device, there is little personal data for us to
        secure. We follow reasonable measures to protect the limited data we do handle.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Children’s privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our tools are general-purpose and not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly
        collect personal information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material changes will be reflected by the
        “Last updated” date above.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? Reach us via the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <AdSlot id="inContent" label="Advertisement" />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
